propDescriptions.aria-label: Defines a string value that labels the current element.
propDescriptions.aria-labelledby: Identifies the element (or elements) that labels the current element.
propDescriptions.component: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.components: The components used for each slot inside the TabsList. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.componentsProps: The props used for each slot inside the TabsList.
